&lt;h3&gt;Wi-Fi Assessment with Controlled Capabilities&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;wi-fi-assessment-with-controlled-capabilities&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
